     $(document).ready(function() {
         $(".jputMPX").each(function() {
             title = $(this).attr("title");
             $(this).val(title);

         $(".jputMPX").focus(function() {
             title = $(this).attr("title");
             if (this.value == title) {
                 $(this).val("");
             }
         }).blur(function() {
             if (this.value == '') {
                 title = $(this).attr("title");

         $(".signinMPX#buttonMPX a").toggle(function() {
             $("#loginMPX").fadeIn();
             $("#buttonMPX a").addClass("butonMPX");

     function() {
         $("#loginMPX").fadeOut();
         $("#buttonMPX a").removeClass("butonMPX");
     });

          Simply search for your mobile on our website, select one of two payment options, 
         either bank transfer or Cheque, and get money in your pocket.

            </p>

            </p>
